OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Flargely dry start to the evening with
OL,7,Fsome brightness. Then becoming cloudy
OL,8,Fwith frequent showers arriving,
OL,9,Fturning wintry later over Shetland.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,12,Fduring the morning, turning to snow on
OL,13,Fthe hills. A drier afternoon with
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Feeling cold.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,17,Fmixture of sunshine and blustery
OL,18,Fshowers on Tuesday and Wednesday, the
OL,19,Fshowers wintry at times. Some rain
OL,20,Fpossible on Thursday. Feeling cold for
OL,21,Fthe time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
